        <mxCell id="legend" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=11;fontColor=#555555;" value="Solid line = ownership FK (parent ┃—●&lt; child).   Gray dashed = cross-cluster link (evidence cited by observations/hypotheses; similar-incident retrieval).   Red dashed = actor FK → users.&#xa;UQ = unique · PK = primary key · FK = foreign key.   Config (valaf.yaml) is file-based, not in the DB.   No exports table — DOCX/PDF/MD/JSON rendered on request from these rows." vertex="1">
